---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';

// 모든 수식을 변수로 격리하여 Astro 컴파일러 에러 방지 (최우선순위: 엔트로피 감소)
const mathMain = "$ f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\displaystyle \\frac{x^2+ax+b}{x-2} & (x \\neq 2) \\\\ 5 & (x = 2) \\end{cases} $";
const mathLimitText = "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} f(x) $";
const mathF2 = "$ f(2) $";
const mathStep1 = "$ 4 + 2a + b = 0 \\implies b = -2a - 4 $";
const mathStep2 = "$ \\frac{x^2+ax-2a-4}{x-2} = \\frac{(x-2)(x+a+2)}{x-2} = x+a+2 $";
const mathStep3 = "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} (x+a+2) = 4+a $";
const mathStep4 = "$ 4+a = 5 \\implies a=1, b=-6 $";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 07. 미정계수의 결정 - 상세 연습</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			/* [표준 디자인 시스템] KaTeX & 모바일 수식 최적화 */
			.formula-box {
				text-align: center;
				margin: 30px 0;
				background: #fff;
				padding: 30px;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
				overflow: hidden;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.math-container {
				width: 100%;
				overflow-x: auto;
				white-space: nowrap;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.katex-display {
				margin: 0.5em 0 !important;
				overflow-x: auto;
				overflow-y: hidden;
			}

			/* [표준 디자인 시스템] 난이도 내비게이션 최적화 */
			.difficulty-container {
				margin-top: 50px;
				padding: 25px;
				background: #f9f9f9;
				border-radius: 16px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.difficulty-list {
				display: flex;
				gap: 12px;
			}
			.difficulty-btn {
				flex: 1;
				padding: 15px;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 12px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				transition: transform 0.2s ease;
			}
			.difficulty-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
			
			.btn-low { background: #eef7ee; color: #2e7d32; border: 1.5px solid #2e7d32; }
			.btn-mid { background: #ebf3ff; color: #1565c0; border: 1.5px solid #1565c0; }
			.btn-high { background: #fff8e1; color: #a0522d; border: 1.5px solid #a0522d; }

			@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
				.formula-box { padding: 15px 5px !important; margin: 20px 0 !important; }
				.katex-display { font-size: 0.85em !important; }
				.formula-box p { font-size: 1rem !important; line-height: 1.5; }
				
				.difficulty-container { padding: 15px !important; }
				.difficulty-list { gap: 8px !important; }
				.difficulty-btn { 
					padding: 12px 5px !important; 
					font-size: 1.1rem !important; 
				}
				body { padding: 10px; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 07. 미정계수의 결정" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🚀 해결 전략 체크리스트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>함숫값 <span set:html={mathF2}></span>가 존재하는가?</li>
					<li>극한값 <span set:html={mathLimitText}></span>가 존재하는가?</li>
					<li>분모가 0이면 분자도 0인가?</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						[핵심 문제]
					</h4>
					<p>함수 $f(x)$가 $x=a$에서 연속일 조건을 이용하여 미지수를 구하시오.</p>
					
					<div class="formula-box">
						<div class="math-container">
							<span set:html={mathMain}></span>
						</div>
						<p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #333; word-break: keep-all;">가 $x=2$에서 연속일 때, $a, b$의 값은?</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Progressive Disclosure: Step-by-Step Solution -->
					<details style="margin-top: 30px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; background: #fff;">
						<summary style="font-weight: bold; color: #e63946; cursor: pointer; padding: 5px;">📝 단계별 풀이 확인하기</summary>
						<div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #eee; color: #444; line-height: 1.8;">
							<p><b>Step 1. 분자 조건 확인</b><br/>분모가 0으로 가므로 분자도 0이어야 합니다.<br/>
							<span set:html={mathStep1}></span></p>
							<p><b>Step 2. 식 대입 및 약분</b><br/>이차식을 인수분해하여 $x-2$를 약분합니다.<br/>
							<span set:html={mathStep2}></span></p>
							<p><b>Step 3. 최종 계산</b><br/>극한값과 함숫값 5가 같아야 합니다.<br/>
							<span set:html={mathStep4}></span></p>
						</div>
					</details>

					<!-- Difficulty Level Navigation -->
					<div class="difficulty-container">
						<p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #333; font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
							🎯 내 실력에 맞는 문제 도전하기
						</p>
						<div class="difficulty-list">
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type07-low/" class="difficulty-btn btn-low">[하]</a>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type07-mid/" class="difficulty-btn btn-mid">[중]</a>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/levels/type07-high/" class="difficulty-btn btn-high">[수능]</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-cont/" class="back-link" style="margin-top: 40px; display: inline-block;">← 유형별 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>

			<div slot="summary">
				<p>미정계수 결정의 핵심은 **'분모가 0이면 분자도 0'**이라는 사실을 통해 식의 형태를 단순화하는 것입니다.</p>
			</div>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
